# Topper Hub Team - Class 10th Quiz Website

This is a Class 10th Quiz Website for the Topper Hub Team, including quizzes on Math, Science, and History, and a leaderboard feature.

## Features
- Subject-wise quizzes
- Leaderboard to track top scores
- Simple and user-friendly interface

## How to Use
1. Visit the website at: `https://yourusername.github.io/topper-hub-team`.
2. Select your desired subject (Math, Science, or History) to start the quiz.
3. View your position in the leaderboard after completing the quiz.

## Technology Stack
- HTML for structure
- CSS for styling
- JavaScript for functionality

